Package: copilot-cat
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libqt6core6, libqt6gui6, libqt6network6, libqt6qml6, libqt6quick6, libqt6quickcontrols2-6, libqt6websockets6
Maintainer: CopilotCat <copilot-cat@github.com>
Description: Desktop pet cat AI assistant for GitHub Copilot
 A desktop pet cat that serves as a visual interface for GitHub
 Copilot via MCP. Features animated cat sprite, speech bubbles,
 and AI chat powered by Copilot (MCP), OpenRouter, or custom commands.
Homepage: https://github.com/copilot-cat
